		<div id="comment_body_64460745"><p>This is what motivates others to meet the desires and to solve the big problems we face.  If some super-genius figured out how to change the entire game, and could easily/sustainably offer the same power for a much lower price.  Well, then everyone wins.</p><p>Everyone except these short-sighted jackasses that can't seem to figure out how to function in the power biz.  Fuck them, and their little Manhattan dogs too.  Let the new player show them how it's done.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64460745">

